{"tid":1917843,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有細佬嘅入嚟","createTime":"2020-03-09T17:21:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T13:25:02.000Z","uid":202557,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1a1e5ff105b1caa8e9108b16d07d61d4e3355be7","tid":1917843,"uid":202557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T17:21:15.000Z","msg":"大家有冇覺得個細佬特別仆街on9<br />\n我果個同我差兩年<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屋企人唔理我都唔係問題 我唔care<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />問題係下下頂住曬 又係度嘈<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前呀媽話再裝修間屋間番兩間房俾我地兩個<br />\n（因為同房訓緊 勁冇私隱）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢竟然話唔駛 老母又真係聽佢講唔搞<br />\n我屌喇我需要個人空間呀 訓得舒服啲hea啲都望撚住曬<br />\n仲有夜晚十點開音箱彈結他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪傻撚咗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />阻撚住曬 兩老仲好似想叫我預錢俾佢娶老婆<br />\n係咪傻撚咗 我一搬到一定頭也不回 唔駛旨意我接濟佢"},{"pid":"6cfddf829f7ae73f856289ebf828ea5a818fe070","tid":1917843,"uid":182222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T17:25:27.000Z","msg":"細個嗰時我都係咁諗<br />\n無時無刻都想打柒條撚樣<br />\n大個之後搬左出去住反而有D掛住以前打打鬧鬧個D日子"},{"pid":"b607bfea6f69f995d85c82cdd894763353ef03df","tid":1917843,"uid":202557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cfddf829f7ae73f856289ebf828ea5a818fe070","tid":1917843,"uid":182222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T17:25:27.000Z","msg":"細個嗰時我都係咁諗<br />\n無時無刻都想打柒條撚樣<br />\n大個之後搬左出去住反而有D掛住以前打打鬧鬧個D日子"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T17:28:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我year 2 喇 佢仲會郁手打我 打到我手腳瘀